name: TAM Airlines 777-32WER PT-MUI Delivery Flight from Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
Happy Heavy Aircraft Friday!
Hey everyone, this is the delivery flight of TAM Airlines' 9th Boeing 777-300ER, departing Paine Field in Everett, Washington, bound for Brazil. Listen to those engines! That's one of my favorite things about my spot at Paine Field - You're so close to the planes that you can really feel the rumble in your chest when those GE-90s spool up! I hope you enjoy :D

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
